○バッチファイルで実行の例

**aaa.bat**
@echo off
echo "START!!!"
powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Unrestricted %USERPROFILE%\Dropbox\PC\Desktop\testt.ps1
echo "Accomplish!!"
pause > nul
exit


**testt.ps1**
function Samp($x, $y){
Write-Host ($x + $y)
}
Samp 1 2
